{"tid":2058453,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"疑因無阻止學生演奏《榮光》 香島中學屈老師「高調」談政治拒續約","createTime":"2020-06-10T07:30:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-11T08:59:01.000Z","uid":8482,"like":10,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"7e457e810be982ab8d1ec08fc649c947d25efdf3","tid":2058453,"uid":8482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T07:30:40.000Z","msg":"直資左校香島中學爆出政治審查風波。該校一名資深教師向師生發公開信，指校方疑因未有阻止學生於音樂考試中選擇演奏《願榮光歸香港》，因而不獲校方續約。該信又指校方要求教師在政治取態上應與校方同一陣線，「不應只保持中立」，形容事件等同白色恐怖。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200610/2RK7MS6N3RNQ6OJ44SG2WDRQXM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200610%2F2RK7MS6N3RNQ6OJ44SG2WDRQXM%2F&d=TNVh%2FXBsTmD9bRjMILuVa7ZiocJRpRWN%2FMrNqpcM%2BY8%3D&h=70374ab6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200610%2F2RK7MS6N3RNQ6OJ44SG2WDRQXM%2F&h=6cc4dba1\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200610/2RK7MS6N3RNQ6OJ44SG2WDRQXM/</a>"},{"pid":"b6a78ff5c859bc35615078e66fddc1b82a5e4b1b","tid":2058453,"uid":6548,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T07:33:33.000Z","msg":"黨校唔意外啦"},{"pid":"cc85b8f5360e2c45eb6108ad311910b62a9ca75a","tid":2058453,"uid":43062,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T07:35:20.000Z","msg":"邊個送仔女去香島讀都係等做藍絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"336fd50ec40baef5171ee366ab26eca19681071c","tid":2058453,"uid":8482,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T07:35:30.000Z","msg":"大清算由公務員同教育界開始<br />\n慢慢咗染紅"},{"pid":"41bb686caed25a2704ce4789df8c1b8aec716de7","tid":2058453,"uid":8482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cc85b8f5360e2c45eb6108ad311910b62a9ca75a","tid":2058453,"uid":43062,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T07:35:20.000Z","msg":"邊個送仔女去香島讀都係等做藍絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T07:36:50.000Z","msg":"家長咪又係為成績推佢哋啲仔女染紅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c8d1d4bcbc0893ad7f582b70abd88b588e0b3b8","tid":2058453,"uid":54800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T08:59:01.000Z","msg":"香島中學一名教師早前向校長及師生發電郵，懷疑校董會認為她的政治立場與校方不一致，及在音樂考試時未有禁止學生演奏校方所指的「不恰當歌曲」，以致不獲校方續約。<br />\n<br />\n本台取得香島中學透過內聯網向家長發的聲明，校方指校董會一貫按既定程序審慎處理教師續約事宜，其中一個考慮因素是教師的教育信念能否貫徹學校的辦學理念，如兩者出現分歧，管理層必定先與教師溝通，作出提醒。<br />\n<br />\n聲明提到，香島中學是傳統愛國學校，教導學生熱愛國家，認同自己是中國人。本台向香港中學查詢事件，暫時未獲回覆。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1531467-20200611.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1531467-20200611.htm&d=TNVh%2FXBsTmD9bRjMILuVa7ZiocJRpRWN%2FMrNqpcM%2BY8%3D&h=99f5cd30\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1531467-20200611.htm&h=13fdb6a2\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1531467-20200611.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好ON9呀.....未有禁止學生演奏...就唔續約...~!!<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}